Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.92,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Follow me Follow you 唯愿相通
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:55.96,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}释放这沸腾热血
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.12,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:01:02.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}战栗在冲突之中 从天而降的堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.64,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}可要过早地将早熟的果实 吞噬殆尽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:13.13,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}几度挣扎 总不忘仰问苍穹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:16.12,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}确认你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:21.07,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}无意与人假装和气 徒增太多恸哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:26.33,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}混乱在纠葛之中 只为活在当下
