Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽在倾听星核之声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽跟人家打招呼说你好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好要说好多好多话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复数机体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将遭到包围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类军 要抓我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是在欢迎我们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保护我们 明明没有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是珀耳修斯中队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四守备队队长沃尔特·巴格斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到斯利那加区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是龙宫岛部队 感谢迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了广域电波通信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这分明有可能吸引Festum过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却完全没有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是靠那星核保佑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位长途旅行辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交替看守机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让任何人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去的时候尽量少带行李
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证随时可以逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热烈欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到斯利那加区 阿格拉基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带各位去住宿地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先缓解下旅途疲劳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 美羽想早点去说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先休息休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强自己啊 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽睡足了的 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那棵大树一直在叫美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们倒也希望她能尽快与星核对话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的工作就是听美羽的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要妈妈同意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说一会儿哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说停就要停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 立上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到警报了？有异常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早就觉醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我皆城乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意被人以母亲的名字相称？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从何时起有意识了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你们追求战斗之时起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤 马上召集史彦和其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先给你做检查…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士去叫一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还走不好路 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 快抱我走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在发展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽 还有出岛的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可能会死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.02,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(70,30)}「乐园 准备中」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.27,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(70,30)}「希望岛上和平 真壁一骑」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 「乐园」咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛的核觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新核在召唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 人类与星核共存于一处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是防备敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们防的是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是世界树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里人称巴尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾米莉存放了星核碎片的古井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指那种打水的井吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过现在不能打水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑 危险呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摄影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请将我们的一切都传达给你们的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是格里高利型而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.95,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,663)}Grigori
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被同化的人类心灵 像幽灵一样彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寄生在我们的星核之上的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人无害的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔卡的水底 是与星核对话的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽要是长大了就能做到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能那样成长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去许多东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有颗好大的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 美羽还太小了不能和它说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次接触就碰到了牵牛星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是美羽还太小了不能对话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核企图让美羽成长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美羽希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没关系 我会保护美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的大家都会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6只阿撒谢尔型之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到奔跑者的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标推测为斯利那加区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 步行者依然在太平洋上移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是在追踪那个岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要警告纳雷因将军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军和那个岛忘却了过去的宝贵牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图进行愚蠢的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动选择与敌人同化 抛弃了身为人类的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从根本上颠覆人类救济计划「三重计划」的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令执行交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕下官直言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳雷因将军在人类军中拥有巨大影响力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要与将军对立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击对象纯粹是被Festum同化的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样通告亚洲舰队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要破坏怪物们召唤来的新星核
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这颗星球重塑为人类的绝对生存圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此作出宝贵牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军也在所不惜吧
