Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧不紧 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊讶什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望核像人一样行动的 不是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让岛的星核学习生死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以为你还没到觉醒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继续保持幼小只有毁灭一途
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和岛的星核都这样考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是追踪岛的阿撒谢尔型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你们选择了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是选择和平 而是为希望而战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我们不该选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会反对你们的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护你们在所选的道路上前进才是我的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立刻去保护美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说危机即将来临吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们参加了新星核的争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争夺…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说世界上的数只阿撒谢尔型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和人类 都必将成为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说皆城乙姬不会说这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是一骑和总士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为两者为一份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 两者你们都打算舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说要他们俩驾驶Mk.Sein和Mk.Nicht吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这等于是要他们去死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑的身体已经…总士也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是对你们的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难和痛楚 仅赐予你们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及有限的生命 一切都是祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要如何祝福世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会听从核的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去的话 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯叔 羽佐间老师 拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一失控的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请使用设置在石棺里的芬里尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.47,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(842,663)}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须担心 我一定会让它们启动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要保护美羽就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是美羽 要守护美羽所希望的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见…还有大家都有危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你们所选择的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能问你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:15:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC发来报告 是阿撒谢尔型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入迎击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner部队在第二指挥者管理下启动系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是总士？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁一骑 皆城总士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人立即开始准备岛外派遣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来给我起名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定我的名字 有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去击退敌人 之后再问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部机体已移动至出击格纳库
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请准备驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 为什么要移动Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 你怎么来CDC执勤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来代替奥尔加小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗交给我们就可以了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是依赖你们嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点害怕 但我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方个体代号步行者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正沿岛的航向直线前来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有护盾展开完毕 迎击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在这里看着战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬有读取大家的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并传达给岛的核与敌人两者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以战斗时也要待在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的力量不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的觉醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤老师说你还没进行检查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你们工作结束后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都会生还的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还能回头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在思考 最后的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左眼没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样 一度失而复返
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了那么多敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你却都要靠Festum的力量来生存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能驾驶Sein和Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们是系统内置型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为了解体还解除了限制器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化现象会相当严酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一失手 我们可能会毁了岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的 有我和你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我决定走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去啊 我说了那么多次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你还…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也迷茫了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 有人教会了我使用生命的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去啊 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你别去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉它一直在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我告诉它身在此处的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 来挽留我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来不听人说话 把我的心搅得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子姐也好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 你也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 手和脚…都好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 几时突破防线的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说防卫部队消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 据称西侧防卫据点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为某种原因停止了机能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急出动基地内所有部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:22:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让护卫部队去守卫D岛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市内出现敌人 是德尔菲妮型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.74,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(770,663)}Delphyne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口叔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 马上全体集合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有美羽…拜托 不要伤害美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.21,0:22:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾为和平而战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论其多么短暂 属于自己的和平就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而如今 为了未知的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们选择了去消耗生命
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------EDCN1---------------------------
